 the FarEast.andM;DBS, while continuing to support both product lines, plans to offer the newarchitecture to its clients &quot;niche by niche,&quot; using the mainframe as theserver, Imlay said.andM;He expects to announce some products before year-end.andP;  &quot;1991 will be a yearof development, and the following will be a year of innovation and rollout,&quot;he said.andO;</TEXT></DOC>